\" type=\"button\">Remove</button><br/>\r\nRemove the ID from <strong>Realtime log service consumer IDs</strong>.<br/>\r\nStop collecting logs for the ID. Then remove the logs.<br/>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<button id=\"hide-managing-panel\" style=\"background-color: #6699ff;\" type=\"button\">Hide Managing Panel</button>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Announcements will be updated on Q&A board, such as turning off MMS server, Monitoring service under construction, etc.</h4>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h4>We restored this function. Available from 11:00 a.m., 20-Nov (Korea Standard Time).</h4><br/>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The MRN you are debugging now. MRN=</a><input id=\"mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" [urlparam attr=\"value\" param=\"mrn-being-debugged\" default=\"\" /]/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">view logs</button><br/>\r\nOnly the logs related to the MRN being debugged are shown.<br/>\r\nFirst, the MRN must be registered in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.<br/>\r\nIn order to regiser a MRN in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>, use the function in <strong>the managing panel</strong>.</br>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding-left: 14.4px;\">MMS\'s Maritime Resource Name: <strong>urn:mrn:smart-navi:device:mms1</strong>. Addresses: <strong>http://www.mywebsite.com:8088</strong>, <strong>https://www.mywebsite.com:444</strong>.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[includeme src=\"https://www.mywebsite.com:444/status\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"1200\" id=\"mms-status\"]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div id=\"invisible-container\" style=\"display: none;\"></div>','MMS status page','','inherit','closed','closed','','62-revision-v1','','','2017-11-21 16:04:23','2017-11-21 07:04:23','',62,'https://143.248.57.144/index.php/2017/11/21/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (454,48,'2017-11-21 16:14:07','2017-11-21 07:14:07','MMS Client API was updated to beta-0.6.1. \nIt is available now. See <a href=\"https://github.com/HaJaehee/MC_MMS/tree/beta-0.6.1-alpha+active\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://github.com/HaJaehee/MC_MMS/tree/beta-0.6.1-alpha+active</a>.\nIf you are using MMS Client API beta-0.6.0, need not update the API. Because it is compatible with MMS server beta-0.6.1.\nThanks.','MMS Client API was updated to beta-0.6.1.','','publish','closed','closed','','4','','','2018-08-23 17:33:55','2018-08-23 08:33:55','',1,'https://143.248.57.144/?kboard_content_redirect=4',0,'kboard','',0);
