INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (479,48,'2017-11-22 19:05:11','2017-11-22 10:05:11','<button id=\"show-managing-panel\" style=\"background-color: #6699ff;\" type=\"button\">Show Managing Panel</button>\r\n<div id=\"managing-panel\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Set a Service Polling Method as Normal. Service MRN=</a><input id=\"svc-mrn-normal\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"normal-polling-button\" type=\"button\">Set</button><br/>\r\nNormal polling is that a MMS client periodically sends polling request to the MMS server.<br/>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Set a Service Polling Method as Long. Service MRN=</a><input id=\"svc-mrn-long\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"long-polling-button\" type=\"button\">Set</button><br/>\r\nLong polling is that a MMS client sends a polling request to the MMS server and waits until a message arrives.<br/>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove a Service Polling Method. Service MRN=</a><input id=\"svc-mrn-remove\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"remove-polling-button\" type=\"button\">Remove</button><br/>\r\nRemove the polling method and set it as the default polling method.<br/>\r\nDefault polling method of a service is normal polling.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Add MNS entry having MRN=</a><input id=\"add-mrn\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">IP=</a><input required pattern=\"^([0-9]{1,3}\\.){3}[0-9]{1,3}$\" id=\"ip\" style=\"width: 160px;\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">PortNumber=</a><input id=\"port\" style=\"width: 80px;\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Model=</a><input id=\"model\" style=\"width: 40px;\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"add-mns-entry-submit\" type=\"button\">Add</button>\r\n<strong>Maritime Name System (MNS) Dummy</strong> saves MRN-locator mapping information entries. It appears under the managing panel.\r\nModel <strong>1</strong> is polling client model. Model <strong>2</strong> is service provider (server) model.\r\nModel <strong>1</strong> need not have correct IP and port number. (e.g. IP=1.1.1.1 and port number=0)\r\nModel <strong>2</strong> must have correct IP and port number that MMS server can access.\r\nBe careful that model <strong>2</strong> may not receive messages due to its firewalls, NAT or line sharer(공유기), etc.\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove MNS entry having MRN=</a><input id=\"remove-mrn\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"remove-mns-entry-submit\" type=\"button\">Remove</button></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Add the MRN you are debugging. MRN=</a><input id=\"add-mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"add-mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">Add</button><br/>\r\nRegister the MRN in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.<br/>\r\nBegin collecting logs related to the MRN being debugged.<br/>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove the MRN you are not debugging anymore. MRN=</a><input id=\"remove-mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"remove-mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">Remove</button><br/>\r\nRemove the MRN from <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.<br/>\r\nStop collecting logs related to the MRN being debugged. Then remove the logs.<br/>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Add the ID consuming realtime log service. ID=</a><input id=\"add-id-realtime-log-ids\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"add-id-realtime-log-ids-submit\" type=\"button\">Add</button><br/>\r\nRegister the ID in <strong>Realtime log service consumer IDs</strong>.<br/>\r\nBegin collecting realtime logs for the ID.<br/>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Remove the ID not consuming realtime log service anymore. ID=</a><input id=\"remove-id-realtime-log-ids\" type=\"text\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"remove-id-realtime-log-ids-submit\" type=\"button\">Remove</button><br/>\r\nRemove the ID from <strong>Realtime log service consumer IDs</strong>.<br/>\r\nStop collecting logs for the ID. Then remove the logs.<br/>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<button id=\"hide-managing-panel\" style=\"background-color: #6699ff;\" type=\"button\">Hide Managing Panel</button>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>We reset MMS server at 18:34 on 22-Nov (KST) in order to resolve fatal issue.</h2><br/>\r\n<h2>Now 19:00 on 22-Nov (KST), because there are too many logs, this page is not working correctly. Please try refreshing with Ctrl+F5. </h2><br/>\r\n<h4>Announcements will be updated on Q&A board, such as turning off MMS server, Monitoring service under construction, etc.</h4>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n\r\n<h4>We restored this function. Available from 11:00 a.m., 20-Nov (Korea Standard Time).</h4><br/>\r\n<a style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The MRN you are debugging now. MRN=</a><input id=\"mrn-being-debugged\" type=\"text\" [urlparam attr=\"value\" param=\"mrn-being-debugged\" default=\"\" /]/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"mrn-being-debugged-submit\" type=\"button\">view logs</button>&nbsp;&nbsp;<button id=\"return-to-status-page\" type=\"button\">return</button><br/>\r\nOnly the logs related to the MRN being debugged are shown.<br/>\r\nFirst, the MRN must be registered in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>.<br/>\r\nIn order to regiser a MRN in <strong>MRNs being debugged</strong>, use the function in <strong>the managing panel</strong>.</br>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding-left: 14.4px;\">MMS\'s Maritime Resource Name: <strong>urn:mrn:smart-navi:device:mms1</strong>. Addresses: <strong>http://www.mywebsite.com:8088</strong>, <strong>https://www.mywebsite.com:444</strong>.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[includeme src=\"https://www.mywebsite.com:444/status\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"1200\" id=\"mms-status\"]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</t